      <title>泰国提高税收优惠并减少禁售期以提振股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/thailand-raises-tax-breaks-trims-lock-ups-in-bid-to-buoy-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国将提高 ESG 重点基金持有人的税收减免并缩短锁定期，以支持受到外国投资者外流冲击的当地股票市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/thailand-raises-tax-breaks-trims-lock-ups-in-bid-to-buoy-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 11:09:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
